PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the use by TRANSGAS LIMITED and by SASKATCHEWAN TELECOMMUNICATIONS of their statutory power to acquire a right-of-way on POUNDMAKER INDIAN RESERVE NO. 114-13 in Saskatchewan, for the purposes of a natural gas pipeline and a telecommunications transmission system, and (b) granting each of them an easement for those purposes, in lieu thereof.
